msgstr ""

#: ../../source/managing_palettes_and_styles.rst:345
msgid ""
"Select the frame you want to check: if the key button ( |Toonz71_141| ) "
"in the top bar of the palette editor is blue, the colors have a key at "
"the current frame."
msgstr ""

